Class VehicleStateManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.VehicleStateManager

  • public class VehicleStateManager
extends Object
    Provides access to the Vehicle State Services. Allows to register / unregister vehicles, query vehicle states, etc.
